"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?5/8/5252/abstract/9\">",
"      Benifla JL, Goffinet F, Darai E, Madelenat P. Antepartum transabdominal amnioinfusion to facilitate external cephalic version after initial failure. Obstet Gynecol 1994; 84:1041.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?5/8/5252/abstract/10\">",
"      Adama van Scheltema PN, Feitsma AH, Middeldorp JM, et al. Amnioinfusion to facilitate external cephalic version after initial failure. Obstet Gynecol 2006; 108:591.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?5/8/5252/abstract/11\">",
"      Cluver C, Hofmeyr GJ, Gyte G, et al. Interventions for helping to turn term breech babies to head first presentation when using external cephalic version. Cochrane Database Syst Rev 2011; :CD000184.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
