"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?5/8/5252/abstract/12\">",
"      Porat S, Amsalem H, Shah PS, Murphy KE. Transabdominal amnioinfusion for preterm premature rupture of membranes: a systematic review and metaanalysis of randomized and observational studies. Am J Obstet Gynecol 2012; 207:393.e1.",
