"      Shirai T, Shimota H, Chida K, et al, &ldquo;Anaphylaxis to Aprotinin in Fibrin Sealant,&rdquo;",
"      <i>",
"       Intern Med",
"      </i>",
"      , 2005, 44(10): 1088-9.",
"     </div>",
"    </li>",
